1
00:00:46,740 --> 00:00:50,980
=The Antidote to Love=
=Episode 8=

2
00:00:58,590 --> 00:01:00,430
(Could there be any news of him here?)

3
00:01:11,460 --> 00:01:14,000
The young master of the Sword Sect
hired killers

4
00:01:14,000 --> 00:01:15,040
but ended up slain himself.

5
00:01:15,040 --> 00:01:18,140
He left behind over 380 foes.

6
00:01:18,140 --> 00:01:19,860
They hope to find the killer
in seven days.

7
00:01:21,020 --> 00:01:22,140
He deserved it.

8
00:01:28,020 --> 00:01:30,840
Pan Wei, the richest in Dawei,
vanished mysteriously.

9
00:01:30,840 --> 00:01:32,360
His family's vault was robbed.

10
00:01:32,360 --> 00:01:33,700
There are three suspects,

11
00:01:33,700 --> 00:01:35,060
and they're his three wives.

12
00:01:35,060 --> 00:01:36,580
His second wife is the most suspicious.

13
00:01:36,580 --> 00:01:39,580
Find the proof of her affair
with the pawnshop owner in three days.

14
00:01:39,580 --> 00:01:40,900
How absurd.

15
00:01:46,400 --> 00:01:47,320
What are you doing?

16
00:01:47,540 --> 00:01:49,080
Helping you sort the news.

17
00:01:53,120 --> 00:01:54,020
Come on.

18
00:01:54,380 --> 00:01:55,830
Do you know the news

19
00:01:55,840 --> 00:01:56,890
is more valuable than gold

20
00:01:56,900 --> 00:01:57,960
to the Star Sect?

21
00:01:58,160 --> 00:02:00,240
If word gets out about this,

22
00:02:00,240 --> 00:02:01,400
your life could be in danger.

23
00:02:03,740 --> 00:02:04,740
I don't really care

24
00:02:05,200 --> 00:02:06,280
about the consequences.

25
00:02:06,440 --> 00:02:08,220
Young Master, a guest is here.

26
00:02:12,860 --> 00:02:14,060
The news you want is here.

27
00:02:36,460 --> 00:02:38,020
You're still alive.

28
00:02:49,040 --> 00:02:51,140
Do you know the crime
of hiding the Consort?

29
00:02:52,760 --> 00:02:54,520
She has her own legs to walk on,

30
00:02:54,520 --> 00:02:56,520
yet you blame me?

31
00:02:56,800 --> 00:02:58,800
If I hadn't tipped you off,

32
00:02:59,200 --> 00:03:00,720
would you know she's here?

33
00:03:09,760 --> 00:03:10,600
Come back with me.

34
00:03:12,400 --> 00:03:13,960
Why should I?

35
00:03:14,700 --> 00:03:15,580
Your Highness,

36
00:03:15,790 --> 00:03:16,800
the city is in turmoil,

37
00:03:16,820 --> 00:03:17,820
and danger is everywhere.

38
00:03:17,970 --> 00:03:19,800
Your life could be at risk
at any moment.

39
00:03:20,220 --> 00:03:21,920
Only His Highness can protect you.

40
00:03:25,600 --> 00:03:27,080
Don't you want to kill me?

41
00:03:27,760 --> 00:03:29,000
Only by staying near me

42
00:03:29,360 --> 00:03:30,380
will you have a chance.

43
00:03:59,180 --> 00:04:00,190
How cruel this is.

44
00:04:30,300 --> 00:04:31,280
Yi Jiu! Hyah!

45
00:04:33,800 --> 00:04:34,660
Hyah!

46
00:04:39,740 --> 00:04:40,640
Yi Jiu!

47
00:05:18,660 --> 00:05:19,920
Yi Jiu!

48
00:05:22,240 --> 00:05:23,860
Yi Jiu.

49
00:05:26,370 --> 00:05:30,400
♪Later, I could only blame the rain♪

50
00:05:30,410 --> 00:05:31,900
Yi Jiu.

51
00:05:35,620 --> 00:05:38,210
♪I can't solve the puzzle you left♪

52
00:05:38,210 --> 00:05:40,580
♪I can't ask you to love me back♪

53
00:05:40,580 --> 00:05:44,700
♪Being so far from you♪

54
00:05:44,800 --> 00:05:45,710
Yi Jiu.

55
00:05:45,710 --> 00:05:47,840
♪The ripples you stirred in my heart♪

56
00:05:47,840 --> 00:05:50,250
♪Would never fade♪

57
00:05:50,250 --> 00:05:54,410
♪I can't erase you from my soul♪

58
00:05:54,590 --> 00:05:58,540
♪I search for you in the misty rain♪

59
00:05:58,560 --> 00:05:59,660
Yi Jiu.

60
