♪I can't erase you from my soul♪

74
00:06:42,120 --> 00:06:42,980
Yun Yao.

75
00:06:42,980 --> 00:06:47,040
♪I follow the sound of the camel bell♪

76
00:06:47,040 --> 00:06:47,930
Yun Yao.

77
00:06:47,930 --> 00:06:51,470
♪And spend the rest of my life
searching for you♪

78
00:06:51,540 --> 00:06:52,880
Yun Yao.

79
00:06:54,620 --> 00:06:55,540
Are you hurt?

80
00:06:58,020 --> 00:06:59,300
What did you just call me?

81
00:07:14,860 --> 00:07:15,700
Yun Yao.

82
00:07:16,560 --> 00:07:17,400
Yun Yao...

83
00:07:23,100 --> 00:07:24,980
Have you remembered everything?

84
00:07:30,580 --> 00:07:32,640
I remember our lives

85
00:07:32,640 --> 00:07:34,060
among the Moon Clan five years ago.

86
00:07:35,200 --> 00:07:36,660
You told me your name was Yun Yao.

87
00:07:38,620 --> 00:07:40,500
You sheltered me,
despite your people's doubts.

88
00:07:41,720 --> 00:07:43,630
You even saved me with your blood.

89
00:07:47,220 --> 00:07:49,760
You dressed me in your unique clothing

90
00:07:50,140 --> 00:07:51,960
and took me to celebrate
the Shangsi Festival.

91
00:07:58,240 --> 00:08:00,060
Under the holy tree of the Moon Clan,

92
00:08:00,860 --> 00:08:02,320
we made so many promises.

93
00:08:03,120 --> 00:08:04,400
I even promised you

94
00:08:05,700 --> 00:08:07,180
that I'd return to marry you.

95
00:08:07,180 --> 00:08:08,020
That's enough.

96
00:08:08,980 --> 00:08:10,660
I don't want to hear anymore.

97
00:08:11,240 --> 00:08:12,780
Why did you

98
00:08:12,780 --> 00:08:14,440
destroy my entire clan?

99
00:08:19,420 --> 00:08:20,920
I wish I knew why myself.

100
00:08:21,180 --> 00:08:22,940
We once loved each other so deeply.

101
00:08:23,480 --> 00:08:25,040
Your people treated me like kin.

102
00:08:25,320 --> 00:08:26,400
How could I ever harm them?

103
00:08:26,400 --> 00:08:27,920
You're still lying to me.

104
00:08:28,460 --> 00:08:29,340
No.

105
00:08:29,680 --> 00:08:31,060
The Moon Clan

106
00:08:31,060 --> 00:08:32,520
lived hidden in the valley

107
00:08:32,900 --> 00:08:34,200
and never meddled with the world.

108
00:08:34,640 --> 00:08:35,940
However,

109
00:08:36,320 --> 00:08:37,640
one night changed everything.

110
00:08:37,840 --> 00:08:39,840
All the men, children,

111
00:08:40,100 --> 00:08:42,450
and elders were slain.

112
00:08:42,810 --> 00:08:46,280
The women were seized
and sent to the Office

113
00:08:46,280 --> 00:08:48,220
and forced to become the lowest slaves.

114
00:08:48,220 --> 00:08:49,840
They suffered day after day.

115
00:08:50,540 --> 00:08:51,780
It's been five years.

116
00:08:52,660 --> 00:08:55,220
I've been repenting for it every day.

117
00:08:55,520 --> 00:08:56,960
Guilt never leaves me.

118
00:08:57,640 --> 00:08:58,600
It was me.

119
00:08:58,820 --> 00:09:00,780
I was the one who brought you back.

120
00:09:00,780 --> 00:09:02,080
It happened because of me.

121
00:09:02,680 --> 00:09:05,560
It was I who brought ruin
to the Moon Clan.

122
00:09:06,120 --> 00:09:07,760
Why did you lie to me?

123
00:09:08,160 --> 00:09:10,280
Why? Why did you deceive me?

124
00:09:10,320 --> 00:09:12,060
Why? Why?

125
00:09:12,060 --> 00:09:13,800
- Why lie to me?
- I'm sorry.

126
00:09:13,800 --> 00:09:15,640
Why? Why did you lie to me?

127
00:09:15,640 --> 00:09:16,500
Why?

128
00:09:16,500 --> 00:09:18,380
Why? Why?

129
00:09:18,460 --> 00:09:19,320
Why?

130
00:09:19,600 --> 00:09:21,260
- Tell me. Why?
- Yun Yao.

131
00:09:21,270 --> 00:09:22,760
Yun Yao.

132
00:09:22,760 --> 00:09:24,630
Tell me why.

133
00:09:24,640 --> 00:09:25,490
Why?

134
00:09:25,490 --> 00:09:26,370
I'm sorry.

135
00:09:27,120 --> 00:09:28,160
I'm sorry, Yun Yao.

136
00:09:28,780 --> 00:09:29,640
I've let you down.

137
00:09:29,650 --> 00:09:31,780
Tell me why.

138
00:09:31,780 --> 00:09:32,940
I'm sorry.

139
00:09:33,060 --> 00:09:34,160
I've failed you.

140
00:09:35,930 --> 00:09:37,310
I've failed the Moon Clan.

141
00:09:37,920 --> 00:09:39,880
I just recalled what happened
five years ago.

142
00:09:40,540 --> 00:09:42,300
But I can't remember

143
00:09:43,060 --> 00:09:44,420
why the Moon Clan was wiped out.

144
00:09:46,620 --> 00:09:48,540
You can't remember?

145
00:09:49,860 --> 00:09:51,010
Your Highnesses.

146
00:09:51,540 --> 00:09:52,760
We've finally found you two.

147
00:09:59,070 --> 00:10:00,580
Let me show you something.

148
00:10:12,280 --> 00:10:13,240
Don't follow us.

149
00:10:35,700 --> 00:10:37,380
(As the clouds drift gracefully beneath)

150
00:10:37,380 --> 00:10:38,660
(The day is as dark as the night)

151
00:10:41,700 --> 00:10:44,140
(The deer calls in joy,
grazing on wild mugwort)

152
00:10:51,800 --> 00:10:53,900
These are the findings
from my years of searching.

153
00:10:54,940 --> 00:10:57,160
Every record tied
to the Moon Clan is here.

154
00:10:57,880 --> 00:11:00,280
But there's no record of me
leading the massacre.

155
00:11:02,800 --> 00:11:04,000
After that incident,

156
00:11:04,270 --> 00:11:05,800
the North Army fell apart.

157
00:11:06,740 --> 00:11:08,270
Those who attacked the Moon Clan

158
00:11:08,700 --> 00:11:09,800
all vanished without a trace

159
00:11:09,800 --> 00:11:10,840
or news.

160
00:11:12,100 --> 00:11:12,940
Yun Yao.

161
00:11:14,320 --> 00:11:16,160
I suspect there's more to this story.

162
00:11:20,540 --> 00:11:24,260
♪Autumn wind stirs gentle ripples♪

163
00:11:24,260 --> 00:11:27,940
♪Before the flowers bloom
and fill the earth♪

164
00:11:28,220 --> 00:11:33,900
♪When snow falls, I sing alone,
yet you're long gone♪

165
00:11:35,380 --> 00:11:39,100
♪The past is never marked with a word♪

166
00:11:39,100 --> 00:11:43,220
♪Alas, fate makes all the decisions♪

167
00:11:43,420 --> 00:11:48,340
♪We're destined to meet
yet not meant to be♪

168
00:11:48,620 --> 00:11:50,900
♪Yet my heart still belongs to you♪

169
00:11:50,900 --> 00:11:52,900
♪Leaving me with wounds that never heal♪

170
00:11:52,900 --> 00:11:56,580
♪Years leave the past behind
and turn us into strangers♪

171
00:11:56,580 --> 00:11:58,940
♪Candlelight flickers,
haunting my quiet mind♪

172
00:11:58,940 --> 00:12:03,020
♪Words by the window
lock in the midnight hush♪

173
